body:
Is SystemVerilog's atoi() function supported by Icarus? This example seems to fail, the error signature is:
- "No function named a.atoi found in this context"
```
module tb;
  string a;
  initial begin
    a = "123";
    $display("HELLO WORLD");
    $display("%d", a.atoi());
  end
endmodule
```

